rdf:Description.dc:title: Equirectangular map of the world - coastlines, graticule, and indicatrices
rdf:Description.dc:description: A map of the world, showing all landmasses with 10 degree graticule and Tissot's indicatrices of diameter 1,000km and spacing 30 degrees. Coastlines precise to 110km.
rdf:Description.dc:creator: Justin Kunimune
